show.title: Women Can Hold up Half the Sky
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/KLmHpz
show.description: In the face of cruel judgment and resistance, Su Zhuo stands tall, proving not just her worth, but the worth of every daughter dismissed by outdated customs. Her battle is not just for herself it’s for every woman who’s ever been told she’s less.Her unwavering spirit not only reclaims her rightful place but also melts the heart of her estranged father, Chen Zhili, leading to a powerful reconciliation. Their reunion becomes a testament to healing, growth, and the unyielding power of a woman’s love and resilience.This is not just a story of survival. It's a triumphant anthem of empowerment,a reminder that daughters, too, can hold up half the sky.
